results.name: Smallest prime dividing the composite number consisting of A089017(n) successive 3's followed by a terminal 1.
program: (PARI) do(lim)=my(v=List());for(n=9,lim+1,if(ispseudoprime(10^n\3-2), next); forprime(p=7,,if(Mod(10,p)^n==7,listput(v,p); next(2)))); Vec(v) \\ tests numbers with A089017(n) <= m; _Charles R Greathouse IV_, Oct 23 2013
